    "name": "午夜兽群",
    "steam_appid": 864170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/5222a312f1b0e31eeb252ca82c45b429.avif?t=1765969621\" width=700 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临，阴影蠕动。高塔如脊骨拔地而起，兽群咆哮、爬行、撕咬。你将化身无情的午夜刀影，在月意渐起时独自攀上塔尖，用链锤、飞刀、喷火器……将这些扭曲的恶灵送回深渊。亲身体验飞刀将怪物四分五裂、十字圣光完全净化的爽快猎杀，越杀越冷，愈战愈强，你悦动的舞步如葬礼上的仪式，更似为他们送终。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/c459de8eb21d11a8ac4ff010b8c02fb8.poster.avif?t=1765969621\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/c459de8eb21d11a8ac4ff010b8c02fb8.webm?t=1765969621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/c459de8eb21d11a8ac4ff010b8c02fb8.mp4?t=1765969621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/f3d025dfa7e60f6f65970be400e217b1.avif?t=1765969621\" width=700 height=147 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >月蚀吟诵你的名字，古老的秘技因此苏醒！圣光对腐朽的宣判、钢铁与血液交缠后的新生……你将在这片被黑暗吞噬的废墟中，塑造属于自己的杀戮风格——以更迅疾的步伐、更灵巧的身法，在层层逼近的兽潮缝隙间穿行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/21f067f2a137818ae9b8b6680695918b.poster.avif?t=1765969621\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/21f067f2a137818ae9b8b6680695918b.webm?t=1765969621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狩猎将解锁教堂圣所的资源与遗物：飞剑化作银光横扫战场、圣罐回复最后一丝生机、秘仪让亡魂之力回归体内，每一次增强都让你更加从容。力量、技巧与秘技不断累积，圣光终将穿破深渊的幕帘。直到永夜崩塌的一刻，你会成为独自伫立在塔尖之上的最后幸存者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/9fffadab8ed4fe6539f5cc72a0f681b2.poster.avif?t=1765969621\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/9fffadab8ed4fe6539f5cc72a0f681b2.webm?t=1765969621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/6b7d3f914ed1874318783c9ff7f3fdeb.avif?t=1765969621\" width=700 height=147 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在断裂的屋脊上奔袭，悬立于高塔外墙之上！纵身跃至另一处断垣残壁，如一缕冷光在黑塔之间疾驰。冲刺、速降、墙跑、滑铲……所有跑酷技巧、打破重力皆与你的杀戮节奏交织，让你在滚烫兽潮中如幽灵般穿行，成为夜的舞者斩杀无形的幽灵，高空俯冲时的动能审判般碾碎敌群，而疾步贴墙的刹那仿佛与夜色融为一体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/97c6a9a90a023a81ea8d41fe68d84887.poster.avif?t=1765969621\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/97c6a9a90a023a81ea8d41fe68d84887.webm?t=1765969621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/dc7e70244deb1c6d9ed58b00d196d886.avif?t=1765969621\" width=700 height=147 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教堂在腐朽与绝望中坍塌，而你将在瓦砾与骨灰之上重新建立秩序！地形不再是束缚，亲手改写的战术作品也会同时成为你未曾染指的狩猎场。当从高处俯瞰被黑暗吞噬的城市，你建造的每一块石砖、每一处结构，都在向兽群宣告：这是属于猎手的圣域，也是属于罪恶的葬场。在巅峰之上召唤圣光，纵身一跃，荡尽脚下所有邪恶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/1dc60058cd59210db47b05f011e632d0.webp?t=1765969621\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/1dc60058cd59210db47b05f011e632d0.poster.webp?t=1765969621\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=218 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的建筑物，合理利用可扭转战局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败午夜兽群的将军们</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中解锁多张地图，阻止午夜兽群入侵城市中心</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁独特的职业，支持不同的游戏风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的跑酷移动系统，让你在被围困的中世纪城市屋顶间穿梭自如</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于任务的元进度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量技能和增益选择，具备协同和融合机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哥特风格的Boss，拥有多样化的攻击模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张地图都可以提升，随着你加入更多具有独特特性和能力的建筑。 </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864170/extras/30f92ee224a97f740f1e1eb5962e1943.avif?t=1765969621\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p>",
